Name: Average time to complete 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' before 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time elapsed from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-Checklist Completed'.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time required for transitioning from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and 'SW-EIC Reject' across all cases.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Reject'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' in the context of the review process.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' to understand its impact on the review process.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time between 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' to gauge efficiency in reviewer assignment.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time for 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' across all variants to identify bottlenecks in the manuscript review process.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' from the start of the manuscript submission process.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Total time it takes 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' after 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to assess the impact of plagiarism checks on the review timeline.

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to identify the fastest progression through this stage.
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Total time from 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' to 'SW-EIC Major Revision' to understand the timeline towards major revisions.
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to assess the impact of declined reviews on the process timeline.
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Average time to complete 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' grouped by manuscript submission month to identify seasonal variations in the review process.
